<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/961511-why-should-we-be-feminists-why-not">Why should we be feminists? Why not egalitarians?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_961511'><a id="like_count_community_question_961511" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/961511?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">70 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F22738563-we-should-all-be-feminists">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/961511-why-should-we-be-feminists-why-not">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/961511-why-should-we-be-feminists-why-not">See all 18 answers</a>
</li>
